  QuestTitle: Trial of Culling 3
  QuestObjective: Kill 50 Minions
  QuestDescription: You are ordered to destroy the Twin Towers with directed energy
    weapons. You must make it look like a hijacked plane that crashed into the towers
    is the real culprit. Blame a couple sand people to placate the masses. This will
    be used as a justification to go to war.
  QuestOutcome: You sense no gratitude will follow your task, only silence... and
    the faint impression that something unseen is taking careful note of how efficiently
    you end a life.
